channel.title: Full Elite
channel.description:
Ok guys, I got bored and thought i would mess around with a few models, and i decided on getting Black Elite into the 317.
I only had enough time to code the male elite. So sorry ladies. Don't worry i have a pic. And its right... about.. [IMG]http://i551.photobucket.com/albums/ii448/badger41badger41/0001.png[/img] there.. :D
I know that Elite doesn't come with boots but these looked like they went with the set so i added them too. These models are animated so they aren't dead models that just float with you.. they move etc.. Now, this is not 100% being 500+ models as they are, you should know that they wont look 100% correct on the 317 character. You may notice the slight bugs in the picture so not much explaining is needed. Before you ask for the ints and what not, I have packed 2 text documents in the download. 1st: this is the model guide, it will tell you which models are what. 2nd: these are the inits, or ints as most people call them, they probably aren't 100% correct but they look fine so yea..
I hope everyone enjoys these. NOTE: I WILL REMOVE IF NOBODY POSTS.
And now for the download link...
http://www.megaupload.com/?d=67RU2942
